{"type":null,"faqId":7678,"title":"如何添加/删除/查看/发送电子邮件？","answer":"<p>1. 添加Email 帐户：进入主菜单-&gt;电子邮件-&gt;选择账户服务商种类-&gt;登录帐号。账户<br />配置分为手动设置和自动设置。<br />&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;1） 手动设置：<br />&nbsp; 输入账号和密码-&gt;点击菜单键-&gt;选择手动设置-&gt;进入设置电子邮件界面，分别进行<br />&nbsp; 接收和发送服务器设置-&gt;点击下一步 -&gt;在账户选项界面可选择收件箱检查频率-&gt;<br />&nbsp; 点击下一步-&gt;进入设置电子邮件界面-&gt;输入账户名称和您的姓名，点击完成。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img width=\"496\" height=\"368\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/resource/cn/Image/wt4-120419095713.PNG\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img width=\"544\" height=\"406\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/resource/cn/Image/wt5-120419095850.PNG\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img width=\"542\" height=\"405\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/resource/cn/Image/wt6-120419095920.PNG\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>2）自动设置:<br />&nbsp;输入账号和密码-&gt;直接点击下一步-&gt;选择账户类型（POP3 或IMAP）-&gt;手机会自<br />&nbsp;动配置接收和发送服务器，然后直接进入设置电子邮件界面-&gt;输入账户名称和您的<br />&nbsp;姓名，点击完成。（自动配置需要手机中预置该类型Email 的参数）。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img width=\"508\" height=\"380\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/resource/cn/Image/wt7-120419100247.PNG\" /></p>\n<p><img width=\"507\" height=\"374\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/resource/cn/Image/wt8-120419100311.PNG\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>2. 删除Email 帐户：进入电子邮件-&gt;按菜单键-&gt;帐户，在要删除的帐户上长按，选择<br />删除帐户。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img width=\"294\" height=\"437\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/resource/cn/Image/wt9-120419100600.PNG\" /></p>","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7818","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1334799208000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":144,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}